listing.notes:
Nacht Der Magier - The Magicians' Night Very rare complete board game in excellent condition.

Innovative board game where the game is played in pitch dark. When playing in the dark, the fire, cauldrons, wizards (used to push pieces) and the ring of light glow, while trees and discs become invisible. The game can also be played in daylight, but it loses a lot of its charm, because it gives its best in the dark.


- In 2006 he won the Deutscher Kinderspiele Preis prize;

- Also in 2006 he received the nomination for the Kinderspiel des Jahres;

- The game won Essener Feder for best game instructions for elaborate illustrated instructions with comics;

- Won the 2006 Swiss Games Prize in the Children's Games category;

- In France, he received the As d'Or - Jeu de l'Année enfants (Child's Play) in 2007.


Multilingual instructions (also in Italian!)
